'''Christian Force''' ({{Lang-es|Fuerza Cristiana}}) is a [[political party]] in [[El Salvador]]. It first contested national elections in [[Salvadoran legislative election, 2003|2003]],<ref name=N1>[[Dieter Nohlen|Nohlen, D]] (2005) ''Elections in the Americas: A data handbook, Volume I'', p280 {{ISBN|978-0-19-928357-6}}</ref> when it received 1.1% of the vote, but failed to win a seat.

