'''Oscar Rolando Cantuarias Pastor''' (13 May 1931 &ndash; 8 November 2011) was the [[Roman Catholic]] archbishop of the [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Piura]], [[Peru]].

Cantuaris Pastor was born in [[Ascope]]. Ordained to the pristhood in 1955, he became a bishop in 1973. He retired as archbishop emeritus in 2006,<ref>[http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/bishop/bcanpas.html Oscar Rolando Cantuarias Pastor]</ref> and died in [[Piura]] on 8 November 2011, aged 80.

